race.comment: Competitive. SURFERS ROYALE (10) found more like his best beaten less than 2L this grade at Eagle Farm. He rides the speed and will be fitter again. Should go close. Graham is off the above and sticks with CASROCK (12), who sits at the bottom of the weights. She's proven third-up and has plenty up her sleeve. Maps well and is a live chance. I SEE YOU COMING (5) ran a big number beaten a whisker in the Surfers Royal race at big odds. Maloney rides today replacing Thompson and will give him every chance from the handy barrier. Thompson is aboard BILLIONAIR BABY (6) who tries hard and relishes wet tracks. A hope bringing his A-game.
